Reasoning: The paper deals with communication systems and specifically with the use of training codes for noncoherent communication in relay networks. This falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also involves the use of space-time block codes (STBCs) and channel estimation, which are topics in communication systems (cs.COMM) and signal processing (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes a strategy for asynchronous relay networks, which involves synchronization and coordination, making it relevant to systems and control (cs.SY).
